Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP KARAOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing... nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's hurry up and start. It's cold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll begin the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's theme is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Final Words of Famous People."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"More light!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose words are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, a quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know? It's a famous person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's that... that one guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, who's really famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bzzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The correct answer was Goethe. The famous literary master, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Goethe. I was just about to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the next one:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to eat something."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He said that before he died?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hint: This person is also a literary master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it must be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that foreign author, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...who wrote that work called something or other...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Bzzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The correct answer is Mr. Soseki Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a big eater, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mr. Ibuse is a villain."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Osamu Dazai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding ding! That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But writing bad things about somebody is a bizarre final testament, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what on earth this guy Mr. Ibuse did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for the "Literary Masters" series.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is the "Sportsman" series.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"The New Year's grated yam was delicious."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's the suicide note of Tsuburaya, the marathon runner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding ding ding ding! Right! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you knew that, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's a famous last testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It also said other things, like the sushi, wine, and squid were delicious, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. It's impressive that you know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Tsuburaya returned to his hometown just before he died,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and ate grated yams with his mother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess maybe everyone wants to go home before they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, now that you mention it, Misaki, are you from this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Cassiopeia, so the North Star is around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that way, a small town looking out on the Sea of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a beautiful promontory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which apparently ever since a certain famous person threw himself off of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,has unfortunately become a well-known suicide spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you're little, you don't know things like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so I played out on that promontory a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, I still dream about it sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I guess it's possible it was just a dream from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if New Year's grated yams are good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sudden, but we're having an exam tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year's final exam that got postponed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a graduation exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I'll end up going someplace far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to ask where I'm going or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To a faraway town that no one knows about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet tomorrow at 12 in front of the station, rain or shine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still on even if it snows!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I will announce the exam result.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You passed with flying colors! Congratulations, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, my project is successfully completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done good work over this long period.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was it me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That you selected for your project?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know that both this park and your apartment, Sato, are visible from my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking outside from my window and I found him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,a person even more worthless than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tatsuhiro Sato, (hereafter Party A), and Misaki Nakahara, (hereafter Party B),
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,hereby agree to the following contract:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,1. Party A will not grow to dislike Party B.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,2. In short, Party A will grow to like Party B.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,3. He will not have a change of heart along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,4. He will never change his feelings in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,5. He will always be at her side when she is lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,6. That said, Party B is always lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so in short, Party A will always be at her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,7. If he does this, life will probably proceed in a good direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,8. I think the suffering will go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,9. If he breaks his promises,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the penalty is millions and millions of yen."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a simple thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat me kindly, and I'll treat you kindly too, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried my very hardest in order to save you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,By now, you're crazy about me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nobody else but me, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't sign it, you'll be all alone forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing is just too empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign it! If you don't, I feel like I'll fall to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do dry-cloth friction rubs or something to toughen your body and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll stop coming up with these kinds of silly ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A pretty girl like you can definitely have a terrific life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up when you walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Aren't you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not lonely~?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you sign the contract~?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she called you a worthless human being?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't have a right to save Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really the only reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings don't want to admit that they're worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they're constantly seeking someone more worthless than themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also why the Internet is overflowing with insults to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,People who couldn't find anyone more worthless than themselves around
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,brand somebody they've never met a worthless human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because they want to believe they're better than someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hollow, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because while they're badmouthing somebody else,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,they can feel comforted that they themselves are all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't actually help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that if, instead, one would just acknowledge that one is a worthless human being,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it might make things easier?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:13:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That you're just a NEET, a worthless human being pitied even by a girl younger than yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, let's just admit it, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just admit it, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Sato, say "Aah."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aah."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah... Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aah."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on! Let me eat that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aah."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Wait for me! Let me eat it! Wait for me! Let me eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me eat it! Let me eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On a certain day in January,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,my living allowance from home was cut off completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tatsuhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father's going into the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so your living allowance will have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And my final hope, the assistance from Yamazaki too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,About what we talked about before, my sending extra cheese and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, there are just a lot of problems with doing that, so I'm calling that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to "ha-ha" about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder how many days it's been since I had a real meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want calories. Anything will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry and rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutlets and rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuna and rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the compound DHA found in tuna stimulates brain activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that eating tuna will unquestionably have a positive effect on your creative activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...unquestionably have a positive effect on your creative activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Question: Why can one keep living as a hikikomori?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer: Because one's food, clothing, and shelter are assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because one is permitted a lukewarm bare minimum of a life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that one can keep living as a hikikomori indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to live as a hikikomori was, in itself, very much a luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the assurance of food, clothing, and shelter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you're prepared to die, there's no other way but to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally escaped from being a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki, hang in there! Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My, I wonder what on earth happened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a lot going on with the Chiba family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she collapsed in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the poor girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sato, from the Mita House, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the landlord for Mita House is you, Misaki's uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met once, at the lease signing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So naturally, that's how Misaki knew where I was from and what college I went to and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, how is Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She got dizzy and collapsed in the bathroom, and that's when she got injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl was my younger sister's only daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Her real father died right after she was born, and after a while my sister remarried,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but that husband was a terrible guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.96,Background2,,0,0,0,,Don't! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He hardly worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And stuff like his getting drunk and raising his hands to his family were everyday occurrences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:04.17,Background2,,0,0,0,,Don't! Come on, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.24,Background2,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the girl's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, it was never clear if it was a suicide or an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl she left behind was alone with a father she was unrelated to,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and apparently had a very hard time of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, she turned into a very socially inept girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I took her in and she started school here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,she couldn't adapt, and before long she quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be feeling like she's a burden on my wife and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's at the age where she probably wants to goof off and wear nice clothes and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,she doesn't indulge herself at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, she does things like accompanying my wife, and working at the manga café I own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, since meeting you, Sato, she'd grown much more cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When that girl talked about you, Sato, she really looked like she was having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird that I should be requesting this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but could you please be a friend to the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&H222222&\frz359.253\fs60.504\b1\pos(793.334,392.5)}Misaki Nakahara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuko's not here either?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're together, there's nothing to worry about, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuko! Kazuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.65,Note,,0,0,0,,Nationwide Railway Timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:10.61,Note,,0,0,0,,The New Year's grated yams were delicious. So to everybody, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She really was sound asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to take your eyes off that girl, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess maybe everyone wants to go home before they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I'm broke, right, Misaki?
